{"tid":1905300,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝229太子手足，香港人，係時候翻嚟啦","createTime":"2020-03-01T07:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T19:41:46.000Z","uid":238660,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d087655a89edb42e885ca09e384ae49ed5250fa4","tid":1905300,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25g9hZV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25g9hZV.jpg&h=bcb8efce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我之前喺度諗香港人去咗邊但係原來大家一直都冇忘記831,琴日我見到嘅係香港人返嚟啦，多謝太子手足<br />\n<br />\n每一場抗爭都係暴動，每一個抗爭者都係挑戰政權嘅恐怖份子，係暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n但係呢個係暴政加諸於香港人嘅罪名，欲加之罪，何患無辭？<br />\n<br />\n歷史係由勝利者寫嘅，赤匪1927年反國民黨嘅反抗，比國民黨形容為秋收暴動，但係毛甴東奪權後即刻改為秋收起義。<br />\n<br />\n所以有一樣野好想講嘅係，香港人，記住。<br />\n<br />\n贏左你就係革命，係起義；贏左你就係革命先驅，係抗爭者。輸左你就係暴動，係反動；輸左你就係暴徒，係恐怖份子。<br />\n<br />\n#革命許勝不許敗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fc28296936b5e4f7093f0219650a0d61d649de","tid":1905300,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:15:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a11e8cd3ec7d9348dbc46a83277ef9f9e6aa780b","tid":1905300,"uid":162724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:17:15.000Z","msg":"琴晚<br />\n我只有一句<br />\n我屌"},{"pid":"1b073e1675dcb8eb41b1c3db93ae98556eced6ed","tid":1905300,"uid":70371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea4f93af9263d408295ea3f2b354d9af4c699079","tid":1905300,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d6d2ae33b2e0a69e611e069460492b920a4707","tid":1905300,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:20:46.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"eaa498b84a0778d09a0d25d108379f4856275a82","tid":1905300,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike"